tps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5626656/165046918-52888dcb-6391-4385-93e3-e6eb58514b6d.png)\r\n\r\nI'd suggest to change the issue title to something like \"Receive Encrypted folders have Watch for Changes enabled and Full Rescan Interval set to 3600 when added using Auto Accept\" or similar.\r\n\r\nThis may tricky to fix though, as Syncthing would have to override the user defaults here. On the other hand, it already does by automatically setting the folder type to Receive Encrypted when auto accepting password-protected folders instead of what's specified in the defaults, so this could probably be treated as an exception. Maybe do this only if the default folder type is not set to Receive Encrypted? If it is though, then just follow what's set in the defaults.\r\n","author_association":"MEMBER","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/syncthing/syncthing/issues/comments/1108228601/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"tomasz1986","id":5626656,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjU2MjY2NTY=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5626656?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomasz1986","html_url":"https://github.com/tomasz1986","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomasz1986/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomasz1986/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomasz1986/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomasz1986/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomasz1986/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomasz1986/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomasz1986/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomasz1986/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomasz1986/received_events","type":"User","user_view_t